comments.body:
We might want a stricter interface than `BucketQuery`. [Documentation says](https://googlecloudplatform.github.io/google-cloud-node/#/docs/storage/1.2.0/storage?method=getBuckets) the query object supports the following properties:

- autoPaginate
- maxApiCalls
- maxResults
- pageToken

[BucketQuery](https://github.com/DefinitelyTyped/DefinitelyTyped/pull/18430/commits/c9426d4f805296a73bd89db430ddae4aca4f8309#diff-ec53266acc87cf05e006f2e54c7104e3R96) has delimiter, prefix, and versions in addition.

```
 +    interface BucketQuery {
 +        autoPaginate?: boolean;
 +        delimiter?: string;
 +        prefix?: string;
 +        maxApiCalls?: number;
 +        maxResults?: number;
 +        pageToken?: string;
 +        versions?: boolean;
 +    }
```

